</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="139" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="10.[1365,2574,2694,3475]" pageId="10" pageNumber="139">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1367,1501,3171,3200]" pageId="10" pageNumber="139">Breeding.</emphasis>
Breeding or nursing female Tyleria Mouse Opossums were collected in February, and juveniles have been collected in January. Other than that, nothing is known about its reproductive biology.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
