<subSubSection lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="140" pageId="10" pageNumber="139" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="10.[1365,2574,2694,3475]" lastBlockId="11.[174,1379,295,447]" lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="140" pageId="10" pageNumber="139">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1367,1721,3407,3436]" pageId="10" pageNumber="139">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. There is a lack of recent information on extent of occurrence, status, and ecological requirements of the Tyleria Mouse Opossum. It is known only from three isolated locations, and these sites are in protected areas.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
